	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A minor nitpick about ESRB ratings: You say Mega Man 1 and 2 and Vs. SMB are "N/A but would be E". For anything that has been rereleased without modification on Animal Crossing (GCN), Classic NES Series (GBA), Mega Man Anniversary Collection (PS2), or Virtual Console (Wii), you can just use that version's ESRB rating.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
